OL,3,CIsland Energy CEO apologises for
OL,4,C'distress' caused after gas leak
OL,6,FIsland Energy's new CEO says they have
OL,7,F"lessons to learn" following a gas
OL,8,Fleak in Jersey on the weekend.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to Le
OL,11,FClos Mourant in St Clement on Saturday
OL,12,F14 December where around 50 homes were
OL,13,Fevacuated.
OL,15,FEngineers discovered a gas pocket in a
OL,16,Fservice duct, which has since been
OL,17,Fvented and the leak fixed.
