OL,3,CIsland Energy CEO apologises for
OL,4,C'distress' caused after gas leak
OL,6,FWith the 2nd anniversary of the Haut
OL,7,Fdu Mont disaster only last week, it's
OL,8,Fbeen a particularly sensitive time for
OL,9,Fthe new CEO of Island Energy to take
OL,10,Fover.
OL,12,FIn his first fortnight in the role,
OL,13,FGraeme Millar, Island Energy's CEO,
OL,14,Fhas had to apologise for the
OL,15,F"distress" caused by this latest
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,FMr Millar explains: "I'd like to thank
OL,19,Feveryone who was affected for their
OL,20,Fforbearance and for their patience.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
