OL,3,CIsland Energy CEO apologises for
OL,4,C'distress' caused after gas leak
OL,6,FMr Millar also explained that despite
OL,7,Fstarting the role this month, he will
OL,8,Fremain committed to the island.
OL,10,FHe explains: "Clearly the gas company
OL,11,Fin Jersey is challenged and someone
OL,12,Fhas to take on that challenge.
OL,14,F"I've lived here on the island for 14
OL,15,Fyears. I feel very much part of the
OL,16,Fcommunity.
