OL,3,CIsland Energy CEO apologises for
OL,4,C'distress' caused after gas leak
OL,6,F"Of that #4 million, nearly half was
OL,7,Fspent in the last 12 months, and
OL,8,Fthat's in common with gas companies
OL,9,Faround the world.
OL,11,F"With any kind of infrastructure, you
OL,12,Fhave to keep spending money to
OL,13,Fmaintain it and that's what we're
OL,14,Fdoing, and the amount we're spending
OL,15,Fis actually accelerating."
OL,17,FResidents evacuated from their homes
OL,18,Fsay they were extremely nervous to
OL,19,Freturn to their properties.
