OL,3,CIsland Energy CEO apologises for
OL,4,C'distress' caused after gas leak
OL,6,FConnie Lopez-Rubio, her two young
OL,7,Fchildren, and her dog were just one of
OL,8,Fthe 50 homes evacuated.
OL,10,FShe says: "I have no memory. My
OL,11,Fadrenaline was so rushed because I was
OL,12,Flike 'Let's just get out'; it's a
OL,13,Fsplit second (decision).
OL,15,F"Even coming back the next day I felt
OL,16,Feerie. All day yesterday I felt like:
OL,17,F'Can I turn the light switch on?'. You
OL,18,Fsmell something and you think 'What's
OL,19,Fthat smell?'.
